        <tr><td>SmartHQ Wi-Fi module replacement</td><td>$220 – $360</td><td>Firmware-resistant cases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Main control board replacement</td><td>$440 – $720</td><td>Post-firmware diagnosis</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor capacitor / starter relay</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>10–14 year common service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Variable-speed compressor (post-warranty)</td><td>$900 – $1,500</td><td>Uncommon before year 12</td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Broader refrigerator cost reference: our <a href="/price-list/refrigerator-repair-cost/">refrigerator repair
        cost guide</a>. Service hub: <a href="/services/refrigerator-repair/">refrigerator repair</a>. For the
